dct_title_s: Map of the counties of Bergen and Passaic, New Jersey : from actual surveys
dct_description_sm: County wall map showing roads, townships, buildings, and householders' names. Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to act of Congress by John E. Gillette in the year 1861 ... for the Eastern District of Pennsylvania." Wall map. Originally printed on 4 sheets now conjoined. Includes insets of cities of Paterson/Passaic/Hackensack, 13 other insets of boroughs/villages, 3 city business directories, and embellished border.
